text: Lee Hae-in may refer to: * Lee Hae-in (actress) (born 1986), South Korean actress * Lee Hae-in (singer) (born 1994), South Korean singer and a member of I.B.I * Lee Hae-in (figure skater) (born 2005), South Korean figure skater * Lee Hae-in (nun) (born 1945), South Korean poet published by Waegwan Abbey * Lee Hae-in, South Korean dancesport medalist at the 2010 Asian Games
title: Lee Hae-in
